{"tid":1288853,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"世界三大惡魔 第一位令所有中國人玻璃心醉滿一地","createTime":"2019-07-05T20:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:00:40.000Z","uid":57898,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0271380b9e96b23bc1e51348734f4fc6f27631","tid":1288853,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T20:28:04.000Z","msg":"世界著名的《新聞週刊》（Newsweek），2000年第一期發表了通過兩年時間，徵集全球一百多個國家中的著名政治家，歷史學家，社會學家等2000千多人的投票評選。<br />\n<br />\n評選出20世紀三個罪大惡極，血債纍纍的最大殺人罪犯，最血腥的三大惡魔！<br />\n<br />\n第一名：毛澤東（屠殺，整死3900萬，餓死4300萬中國人）<br />\n第二名：史達林（屠殺2000萬蘇聯人）<br />\n第三名：希特勒（屠殺600萬猶太人） <br />\n<br />\n（編按：文章轉載自網路，有興趣的朋友可到圖書館借閱《新聞週刊》『Newsweek』2000年第一期。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4oxbiR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4oxbiR.png&h=1fa37a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第四位係咪淋病？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4eba23d613419f1401b7d59978763fa8352a6721","tid":1288853,"uid":20640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T20:31:46.000Z","msg":"嬴國又嬴"},{"pid":"e571e9fa1de13b5a3eb618e60d36b8dddf0893fe","tid":1288853,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T20:52:58.000Z","msg":"毛魔剩係計咗1949年之後嘅數字，都仲未計民初由佢策劃嘅叛亂所害死嘅人"},{"pid":"157f857670dc26e0fc4d6b5f4a024bc6ae5ce762","tid":1288853,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5b13a9c7eca36781d644adfdccb0561ca9f9fd","tid":1288853,"uid":190617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T20:59:39.000Z","msg":"我想知班玻璃心點睇E個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467232c1fcbf560eff0f293848b255d41ac53700","tid":1288853,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"